WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:00.966
Mr. Lin

2
00:00:00.966 --> 00:00:04.366
You are indeed the successor I personally selected

3
00:00:04.966 --> 00:00:06.466
Well done this time

4
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:08.066
I am very pleased.

5
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:10.900
Put the Senluo Hall in your hands

6
00:00:11.133 --> 00:00:12.866
I feel at ease

7
00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:14.400
Master really wants to retire

8
00:00:14.933 --> 00:00:16.266
You know it.

9
00:00:16.866 --> 00:00:18.900
The war three years ago

10
00:00:19.133 --> 00:00:21.633
Qinghe's father passed away tragically

11
00:00:21.766 --> 00:00:23.966
I also suffered serious internal injuries

12
00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:25.466
In the past three years

13
00:00:25.733 --> 00:00:28.466
Although I have been carefully conditioning

14
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:31.000
And it didn't quite work.

15
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:33.500
But I grew this year

16
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:34.900
As short as a few months

17
00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:37.433
I don't have much time left.

18
00:00:37.733 --> 00:00:39.433
You don't tell me to let them

19
00:00:39.733 --> 00:00:41.866
Just let me leave with dignity

20
00:00:41.933 --> 00:00:43.100
Master, where are you?

21
00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:43.933
Doctor Hua is with me

22
00:00:43.933 --> 00:00:45.500
I'll bring him to you right away

23
00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:48.566
No, I've run out of oil.

24
00:00:48.866 --> 00:00:51.000
Fire God Doctor is also helpless

25
00:00:52.733 --> 00:00:54.833
I know about Qinghe's father's death

26
00:00:54.866 --> 00:00:56.433
It affects you a lot.

27
00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:59.166
Make you tired of the life of fighting and killing

28
00:00:59.466 --> 00:01:01.200
I don't want to pick up Chang Senluo Hall

29
00:01:02.133 --> 00:01:04.233
But I got to tell you something.

30
00:01:04.466 --> 00:01:05.766
Country in trouble

31
00:01:05.800 --> 00:01:06.966
Everyone is responsible

32
00:01:07.533 --> 00:01:11.200
With your ability, you shouldn't be indifferent to things

33
00:01:11.266 --> 00:01:12.500
Defend the country

34
00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:15.400
It is your unshirkable responsibility and mission

35
00:01:15.766 --> 00:01:16.966
Master, don't worry.

36
00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.366
With me Mulinlong

37
00:01:18.366 --> 00:01:20.400
Never let the deduction enter our country

38
00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:21.700
mess me up

39
00:01:22.333 --> 00:01:25.566
So you are willing to take over the Changsenluo Temple?

40
00:01:25.966 --> 00:01:28.766
I would like to not regret it.

41
00:01:28.866 --> 00:01:30.200
Serve the country with heart

42
00:01:30.966 --> 00:01:32.466
Die without regrets

